abstract: >-
  Structured, research-backed playbooks for AI agents — built with scientific
  rigor and validated through controlled trials. The first playbook,
  angle-gen-kit, generates vocabulary-diverse research angles from a 1-2
  sentence topic, validated across 22 inputs (Q7 avg 3.0/3, Q5 avg 2.82/3).
